fields.Name: Skip AssociationDB - Course Performance with Enrollment Cohorts
fields.Description: Tests Skip's ability to rank courses and break down completion rates by enrollment period (quarter-based cohorts).

InputDefinition.userMessage: Show me the top 10 courses by enrollment, and for each course, break down completion rates by the quarter students enrolled. Present this with a summary table and supporting charts.

judgeValidationCriteria: Response includes top 10 courses ranked by enrollment
Completion rates are shown by enrollment quarter for each course
Both summary and detailed views are provided
Completion rates are calculated as percentages
